<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Bid was Accepted - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .success-badge {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations!</h1>
        <p>Your bid has been accepted</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="success-badge">
            <h2>ðŸš› Bid Accepted</h2>
            <p>Your bid for booking <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong> has been accepted by the shipper.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Hello <%= carrierCompany %>,</h2>
        
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your bid for Shipment with ID <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong> has been accepted. Below are the details of the shipment:</p>

        <div class="booking-details">
            <p><strong>Final Amount:</strong> â‚¦<%= finalAmount %></p>
            <p><strong>Pickup Date:</strong> <%= pickupTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> <%= deliveryTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Shipper Company:</strong> <%= shipperCompany %></p>
            <p><strong>Shipper Contact:</strong> <%= shipperContact %> - <%= shipperPhone %></p>
            <p><strong>Your Contact:</strong> <%= carrierContact %> - <%= carrierPhone %></p>
        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="<%= bookingUrl %>" class="button">View Booking Details</a>
        </center>
        
        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Review the booking details and confirm your readiness</li>
            <li>Contact the shipper to coordinate the pickup and delivery</li>
            <li>Ensure all necessary documents are ready before pickup</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Need Assistance?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need support, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a>.</p>

        <p>Thank you for using IpTruck. We wish you a successful trip!
        <br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
